Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在身處天神卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是熬過了纜車和登山吊椅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳的登山終於正式開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色絕佳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這個天神卡我們已經爬了1500米了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳是1977米 我們要去那裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳的兩個山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做TOMA之耳 和OKI之耳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是因為這兩個山頂很像是貓耳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才起了這樣的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是TOMA是山的入口 OKI是裏面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山中小屋叫做肩之屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩？貓有肩膀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到貓咪的肩膀那裏要沿著山脊走過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和日向的約定很快就要實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次在那座山上看日出的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1088,607)}「成為朋友？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上吃的飯最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好攝取能量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 剛才謝謝你幫我撿票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是纜車搭乘處的那個孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保佑我平安登頂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保佑我能夠看到美麗的日出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保佑世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保佑我能見到小群馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是下坡路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比爬坡輕鬆 多好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下坡的話還得把下坡的部分再爬回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山一開始很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花兒好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有蟬聲還有蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有蝴蝶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道是什麼季節了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到山頂為止還有3.3公里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看數字的話好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊 是不是比剛才增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種小事就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 日向 楓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實今天是心夏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 到了山中小屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面很難走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很難走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 變艱難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這點小事可難不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種路真虧我們小時候能爬上來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小時候身子輕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟富士山比起來 這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點心 點心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊穴澤 有熊先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羊羹好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又吃羊羹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是老爺爺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走一步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 我在上面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是從哪裏來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是從琦玉的飯能來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是群馬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍子好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我今天來的時候坐電車路過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我說了什麼話惹她生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以跟著她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越來越遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子不會察言觀色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天狗的滯留處？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一次到這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拍過好幾次照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要拍這種景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要長時間待在喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就走得快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了什麼樣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是以前拍的谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再看見這樣的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了隨時都能看得見 一直放在相機裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要爬山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因 因為開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 我是來看日出的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是和朋友的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經幾次留宿在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是清晨沒有放晴也很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會出霧 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看見就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫葵 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺自己都變成了天狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫做穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教 我叫日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是楓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香也要留宿山中小屋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 一起吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像是不喜歡與人交往的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說不定不是那樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雲的走向很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪日向說希望下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是懺悔巖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神大人也會在這裏懺悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上雨衣比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包也不要忘了用雨具遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是日向的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有言靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連心夏也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向也懺悔下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我這是向誰道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到山中小屋還有一點點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心腳下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽給我買的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走起來好輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通氣性也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 雨衣確實很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 真的謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好能幫到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這鍾我也有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大雨天真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請在晚餐準備好之前休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡覺請用上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 葵
